items.title: How do I create an account?
items.description: To create an account, tap on the 'Sign Up' button on the login screen, fill in the required details, and follow the prompts to complete the registration process.

items.title: How do I reset my password?
items.description: If you've forgotten your password, tap on the 'Forgot Password?' link on the login screen, enter your registered email address, and follow the instructions sent to your email to reset your password.

items.title: How can I edit my profile information?
items.description: To edit your profile information, go to the 'Profile' section from the main menu, tap on 'Edit Profile', and update your details as needed.

items.title: How do I place an order?
items.description: To place an order, browse through the products, add the desired items to your cart, and proceed to checkout by following the on-screen instructions.

items.title: What payment methods are accepted?
items.description: We accept Cash on Delivery now and online payment soon.

items.title: How long will it take for my order to arrive?
items.description: Delivery times vary depending on your location and the shipping method selected. Estimated delivery times are provided during the checkout process.

items.title: Do you offer international shipping?
items.description: No, we will start international shipping soon

items.title: How do I find the right part for my vehicle?
items.description: Use our search feature to enter your vehicle's make, model, and year, or browse through our categories to find the right parts.

items.title: Can I get more information about a product?
items.description: Yes, you can find detailed information about each product on the product detail page, including specifications, compatibility, and customer reviews.

items.title: How do I contact customer support?
items.description: You can contact our customer support team through the 'Contact Us' section in the app, via email at praveen.codeedex@gmail.com, or by calling our helpline 0466-786546.
